verbose_text: Compared with control groups, the group treated with Oenothera showed that urine protein excretion was reduced, serum cholesterol was decreased, levels of PGE 1 and PGE 2 were increased in renal cortex and medulla, 6-keto PGF 1 -alpha was increased in cortex, and thromboxane 2 production was increased at only 4 weeks after nephrectomy.
